  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Supporting the Government of Zambia to inventory and improve management of their Ivory Stockpiles</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">In adherence with the Convention on International Trade in Endangered Species (CITES) Resolution 10.10, all countries are expected to report a national inventory of ivory stockpiles. This grant will support independent experts to plan and conduct an inventory of Zambia&#x2019;s ivory and to create a long-term data management system. All activities will be conducted with appropriate Zambia government officials, who will be trained to carry on annual inventories and upkeep the database in future.</narrative>
  </description>
